00:00:27.369 --> 00:00:30.570
The first exercise, what we gonna do is stand
up like this, pick up the weights.

00:00:30.570 --> 00:00:37.840
Now as you can see here the weights are very
light, we are using only 15 lbs because we

00:00:37.840 --> 00:00:45.160
are doing shoulders raises with our arms straight
to the sides and front.

00:00:45.160 --> 00:00:53.990
I am going to show you the exercises and just
follow along with me.

00:00:53.990 --> 00:01:07.990
First just stand feet and shoulders like this,
like so, raise your arms up like this and

00:01:07.990 --> 00:01:18.020
coming back to the side slowly.

00:01:18.020 --> 00:01:33.770
Now, you don't have to raise it too high,
just up to your shoulders level.

00:01:33.770 --> 00:01:50.850
Now, for the next exercise, you gonna do the
same techniques but you're going to raise

00:01:50.850 --> 00:01:56.299
