00:01:57.299 --> 00:02:33.870
If you want to make the exercise more interesting,
what you want to do is to combine the shoulders

00:02:33.870 --> 00:02:36.030
raises two of them together.

00:02:36.030 --> 00:02:48.150
You raise to the sides and then you raise
to the front, what you got to is alternate

00:02:48.150 --> 00:02:50.590
them, like so.

00:02:50.590 --> 00:02:53.030
Pick up the weight.

00:02:53.030 --> 00:02:55.190
Make sure you maintain good posture, back
straight, feet and shoulder width apart.

00:02:55.190 --> 00:03:06.780
From there you raise to the sides first, slowly
down, and then you raise to front, down.

00:03:06.780 --> 00:03:12.129
Then to the side.

00:03:12.129 --> 00:03:24.239
Make sure you maintain your breathing.

00:03:24.239 --> 00:03:41.720
For this exercise you can do 3 set of from
6 to10 receptions is very good, so make sure

00:03:41.720 --> 00:03:45.830
